  "prompt": "Where can I find a free online course to learn WordPress themes management?",
  "response": "There are several platforms where you can find free online courses to learn WordPress themes management. Here are some of the best options:\n\n1. **WordPress.org Official Documentation**: \n   - The WordPress Codex (https://wordpress.org/support/) is a comprehensive resource that includes tutorials and guides on managing WordPress themes.\n\n2. **YouTube**:\n   - YouTube hosts numerous free tutorials and courses on WordPress themes management. Channels like \"WPBeginner,\" \"Darrel Wilson,\" and \"WPCrafter\" offer high-quality content.\n\n3. **Udemy**:\n   - Udemy often offers free courses on various topics, including WordPress. Search for \"WordPress themes management\" and filter by free courses. Example: \"WordPress Theme Development & Customization\" (free promotional periods).\n\n4. **Coursera**:\n   - While Coursera primarily offers paid courses, you can sometimes audit courses for free. Look for courses on web development or WordPress.\n\n5. **LinkedIn Learning**:\n   - LinkedIn Learning offers a free trial period during which you can access courses on WordPress themes management. Example: \"WordPress: Building Themes from Scratch Using Underscores.\"\n\n6. **W3Schools**:\n   - W3Schools (https://www.w3schools.com/) offers free tutorials on web development, including some WordPress-related content.\n\n7. **Skillshare**:\n   - Skillshare offers a free trial period, during which you can take courses on WordPress themes management. Example: \"WordPress Theme Development: Create a Custom Theme from Scratch.\"\n\n8. **Google Digital Garage**:\n   - Google Digital Garage (https://learndigital.withgoogle.com/digitalgarage) offers free courses on various digital skills, including web development.\n\n9. **OpenLearn by The Open University**:\n   - OpenLearn (https://www.open.edu/openlearn/) offers free courses on a variety of subjects, including some web development courses that cover WordPress.\n\n10. **Codecademy**:\n    - Codecademy offers free coding lessons, including some that cover WordPress and theme management.\n\nWhen searching for courses, be sure to read reviews and check the course content to ensure it meets your learning needs. Happy learning!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
